profile:
Welcome to Open Canopy Tree Co!
At Open Canopy our goal is to help you beautify your biggest investment, your home. Starting with your yard we can give you an assessment on all of your trees and suggest ways to improve their health and visual appeal, or if need be a complete removal. Open Canopy Tree Co.is focused on providing high-quality service and customer satisfaction – we will do everything we can to meet your expectations. With a variety of offerings to choose from, we’re sure you’ll be happy working with us. Look around our website and if you have any comments or questions, please feel free to contact us for a free estimate.
To expedite the process, please email a photo of the trees you'd like us to look at to info@opencanopytree.com, subject title: Your name + Homestars request

profile:
PROFESSIONAL LANDSCAPING, BEAUTIFUL RESULTS, AND SATISFIED CUSTOMERS!
Since we founded Ramshaw, our team has had the opportunity to work with landscaping, concrete, home building, and renovation companies, along with homeowners, plumbers, electricians, and commercial builders.

We’ve also had the chance to give back to the community, working with local governments to install rock walls in town parks and remove snow from properties.

At Ramshaw, we believe in approaching every project with a professional, hard-working attitude. Attention to detail is at the core of what we do. Hire us for your project, and you’ll be in the hands of pros who value your time and money.

OUR ADVANTAGES
1. At Ramshaw Services we transform Landscapes into quiet places of intimate reflection and a perfect setting for family gatherings or entertainment.

2. We provide detailed installations with outstanding workmanship, as we strive to achieve the best results possible for your Landscape projects.

3. Whatever your needs or desires, we will work with you; whether you have a new site or renovation of an existing landscape, we are excited to create a beautiful outdoor space for you to enjoy.

4. Whether this is new construction or a reimagining of an old site, Ramshaw Services can work with your contractor, landscape architect, project manager, property manager or restoration contractor to co-ordinate services and complete the project in a timely manner at a reasonable price. For many projects we can act as designer and contractor, and complete the entire job.


Please check us out here as well:  https://www.facebook.com/wegetdirtyforyou/
